  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/899150/extras/5af6fbbad3fd63ce518589f7753754ab.avif?t=1643377474\" width=600 height=340 /></span><br>Audio Editor is a professional audio and music editor. With Audio Editor you can edit and record music, voice, and other audio recordings. You can edit audio files with tools like cut, copy, paste.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/899150/extras/37399785b513865f9e1bc24c41612afd.avif?t=1643377474\" width=600 height=294 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Supports Multiple Formats</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Input: Wma,  mp3,  flac,  m4a,  Wav, Aac<br></li><li>Output: Mp3, Wav, Wma, Aac</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/899150/extras/dc496ab3f129e57949f6b2e0027334c2.webp?t=1643377474\" width=600 height=55 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Simple Editing tools</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Simple and fast audio editing using copy, paste, cut and delete.</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Record Your Audio</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Record music, voice, and other audio.</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/899150/extras/45d96f11ea588125816c100669bad9d1.webp?t=1643377474\" width=600 height=55 /></span><br>Edit your audio files in the simplest way - it’s all here, on your desktop!",
